name: Cafe Amelie
html: Beautiful courtyard for outdoor dining and some great food in the quiter end of the French Quarter.

name: Sylvain
html: Converted carriage house with an lively candlelit dining room and courtyard that also serves brunch.  We really enjoy the atmosphere and the food and drinks are stellar.
